{"tid":1416420,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係 \"敵人反對的我們就擁護\" 咩？","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:49:39.000Z","uid":87988,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9e92bd2ed93e2c4ff0783feff20767a69c70a8f7","tid":1416420,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"點解林奠講完反對 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n連登仔就個個咁聽話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要一晚之間洗到成版都係<br />\n你地覺得有無古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b3d404070ed78ebfd8f0bd437d042b70c2513d","tid":1416420,"uid":87988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cff3ac0c4ca4b76f1b4ccbca98087da511a9771","tid":1416420,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bbcf9f2bc4dec91fe1e24a18ab1ea2e7ff35d6","tid":1416420,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af844d6d83d27111142126c95f9bbe410b33f414","tid":1416420,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"用下腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係下下都要跟晒呢句"},{"pid":"3f726fc8ba0c0eedf31dfb752a9d42bf4ad5ebbd","tid":1416420,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"淋奠係提醒我哋唔好比人以呢句口號為借口等大陸狗有位入"},{"pid":"fddca9ff23dbe69c3e9eaa9326cabd864c4951ee","tid":1416420,"uid":195485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"因為敵人講緊我哋無留意到嘅缺點出嚟<br />\n既然係咁我哋好應該改善令到我哋吸納更